{"tid":1057006,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美欲切斷馬杜洛財源 要求印度不買委內瑞拉石油","createTime":"2019-03-11T14:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T15:20:05.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7bb579da1c05fe9284bf648b25aef36cb2459581","tid":1057006,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:50:31.000Z","msg":"（中央社華盛頓10日綜合外電報導）川普政府本週揚言會有更多制裁，以切斷委內瑞拉總統馬杜洛的財政來源，負責處理委內瑞拉危機的美國特使今天表示，美國正在施壓印度，要求停止向委國採購石油。<br />\n<br />\n美國特使艾布蘭（Elliot Abrams）告訴路透社：「我們認為你們不應協助這個（馬杜洛）政權，你們應站在委內瑞拉人民這一邊。」<br />\n<br />\n艾布蘭表示，川普政府對其他政府已發出相同訊息，也對外國銀行，以及其他和馬杜洛有生意往來的公司行號提出類似要求。<br />\n<br />\n美國和支持委國反對派領導人瓜伊多（Joan Guaido）的區域同盟，都威脅施加更多制裁，切斷馬杜洛政府的收入來源，以迫使他下台。<br />\n<br />\n印度市場對委內瑞拉經濟的至關重要，因為印度過去一直是委國第2大現金購油的客戶，僅次於美國。<br />\n<br />\n而美國透過制裁馬杜洛，將大部分石油收入控制權移交給瓜伊多，美國要求印度也比照辦理。<br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉另一主要石油進口國中國，並不以現金採買，中國政府貸款數十億美元給委國，作為購油支付方式。（譯者：紀錦玲/核稿：陳昱婷）1080311<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201903110026.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201903110026.aspx&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6J6X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=3929f05d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201903110026.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"a2e953fc0794ce180efabc387322114a13f71b7b","tid":1057006,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:02:05.000Z","msg":"金正恩都無事，唔驚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020ae88b5293693033e1ffbe1c8073360f50a718","tid":1057006,"uid":240398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2e953fc0794ce180efabc387322114a13f71b7b","tid":1057006,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:02:05.000Z","msg":"金正恩都無事，唔驚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:07:17.000Z","msg":"北韓有反對派咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43a1a2ab25129353f9d7464b46871095db8d58a","tid":1057006,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}